<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM11.8.4">
<l>uruvār piṟavik kaḷiṉṉam pukappeytu</l>
<l>tirivā yeṉṟucin tittiyeṉ  ṟataṟkañci</l>
<l>yirupā ṭerikoḷ ḷiyiṉu ḷeṟumpēpōl</l>
<l>urukā niṟkumeṉ ṉuḷḷamū ḻimutalvā.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Fearing that, dumping [me] again into bodily births,</l>
<l>You think [of me], saying, ‘Wander [eternally]!”</l>
<l>Like an ant on a burning stick with flames at both ends,</l>
<l>My mind keeps melting, primeval of the cosmic dissolution.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
